description.en:
"AlgOil™ - proprietary specialty chemical, which can be custom engineered to be used as a contributory component of products across multiple market sectors.          

Top uses for these specialty chemicals include: high value algae derived products center around nutritional  supplement Omega3 for human and animal consumption, emerging growing application of algae products in the pharmaceutical sector manufacturing antimicrobials, antivirals and anti-bacterial medicines, neuroprotective products,human therapeutic proteins, cosmeceuticals, food, beverage and non-edible form of feedstock for advanced biofuels.                                                                                                                                                                                                                    

Future uses could include drugs for cancer treatment, pharmacology, retina surgery, cannabinoid and cannabinol, diatom fuel cell for solar panels, fuel cell for photovoltaic batteries and bioplastics."
